      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Lindy Cameron is DFID’s Director General for Country Programmes.  Until December 2015 she was Director, Middle East, Humanitarian and Conflict.
Lindy has had a number of other roles in DFID and the UK Government, including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Director, Stabilisation Unit (2012 – 2014)</li>
  <li>Head, DFID Middle East and North Africa Department (2011 - 2012)</li>
  <li>Director, Helmand Provincial Reconstruction Team (2009 - 2010)</li>
  <li>Deputy Director Africa, Trade, Development & International Institutions, Cabinet Office (2008 – 2009)</li>
  <li>Deputy Director, DFID Afghanistan (2006 – 2007)</li>
</ul>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3191">
            <h1 id="director-general-country-programmes">Director General, Country Programmes</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General for Country Programmes is responsible for overseeing DFID’s programmes in Africa, Asia, the Caribbean and Overseas Territories.</p>
</div>
